short_description: Amitaba é un Tour Operator italiano. La nostra attività si basa su un'approfondita conoscenza delle culture extraeuropee, motivata dal desiderio di incontrare popolazioni lontane dalla civiltà post industriale e di muoversi negli spazi dove queste vivono quali: l'India, l'intero arco dell'Himalaia e il Karakorum, l'Altopiano Tibetano, la Mongolia , il deserto del Sahara e il Medio Oriente, fino al sud est dell'Asia, Africa, Patagonia, Ande, Nordamerica e zone Artiche... short_description: This company will be an upscale thrift shop that still caters to everyday people looking for great deals. We will follow the business profile outlined, and offer something for everyone, from high end antiques and art, to middle of the road clothing and accessories at great prices. In tough economic times people turn to thrift shops to help reduce their expenditures and alleviate financial burden. The upside here is slightly used secondhand items often times are of better quality than the newer big box store items and only a fraction of the cost. Our business plan shows clear financial gains within the first year, and profit margin increases over the next 3-5 years. Thrift stores cater to parents looking for deals, older people who can't afford new, and even antique dealers looking for a great price for a resale item. Over 20 percent of Americans currently shop at thrift stores, with another 30 or so shopping at antiques stores, combining the two would give us a bigger audience.
